### Testing Strategies

```cpp
// 1. Exhaustion test
for (size_t i = 0; i < capacity; ++i) {
    assert(pool.allocate() != nullptr);
}
assert_throws(pool.allocate());

// 2. Reuse test
T* obj1 = pool.allocate();
pool.deallocate(obj1);
T* obj2 = pool.allocate();
// Likely obj1 == obj2 (reused)

// 3. Thread-safety test (TSan)
